{"tid":1619163,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"緊急法架空立法機關 宣佈正式要有據點建立臨時議會 重奪三權分立","createTime":"2019-10-04T07:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:56:30.000Z","uid":90306,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"73f53abc31bba7b810af6ce503901a8b5d6f6cb0","tid":1619163,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:27:31.000Z","msg":"既然緊急法出爐，可以用特首權力隨時立法，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>正式立法機關已經被完全架空</strong></span><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足們第一件事就應該正式成立臨時議會</span></div><br />\n方向有二<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 証明緊急法破壞基本法規定政制</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n基本法第73條規定香港特別行政區立法會先係合憲制定、修改和廢除法律<br />\n基本法第43條規定香港特別行政區行政長官只可以簽署立法會通過的法案，公布法律<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%89%E6%AC%8A%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E7%94%A8-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E8%A6%8F%E4%BE%8B%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%97%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581%25E8%25A6%258F%25E4%25BE%258B%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%2597%258E%2F&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7Tof7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=f1c6de79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581%25E8%25A6%258F%25E4%25BE%258B%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%2597%258E%2F&h=514bbefe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%89%E6%AC%8A%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E7%94%A8-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E8%A6%8F%E4%BE%8B%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%97%8E/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2. 以正義之師之名，重奪三權分立高度自治</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n既然行政僭權，政府無法再正常合法地服務人民，應該正式成立屬於人民嘅臨時議會補救<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">【香港臨時議會】今日正式成立！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606510</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論據點係現實地點還是網上，一定要大大力推動臨時議會嘅正當性，我咃係維護法治、保護香港政制完整，以人民之名，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命。</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"48566ef74a272e2c8495d3ba75e92807e671cad6","tid":1619163,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:29:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"118fc1fe403f9d327a3288bdd2c63c59bc9b3e8b","tid":1619163,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:30:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"83b9274cbe2f8096a0a1b1a0ec611c23860373cc","tid":1619163,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:31:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a47d56aaf0867f611ecf7758d23f1d5d88618075","tid":1619163,"uid":90306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a684c90db912baac7a17fdec27c6e350bd6420b3","tid":1619163,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:33:16.000Z","msg":"官迫民反 還政於民"},{"pid":"4d58f4f18ee2721a9fccfb82706e610c24bbf748","tid":1619163,"uid":272454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"d1c02435dee6ad492777b3d3bede89a2ad85b58a","tid":1619163,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"<span s